FQuotes: Every step you take is a step towards your goal.
The journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step.
Don't count the steps, make the steps count.
Believe in yourself and all that you are. Know that there is something inside you that is greater than any obstacle.
The only way to do great work is to love what you do.
You're stronger than you think, keep pushing.
Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts.
It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop.
If you want to achieve greatness, stop asking for permission.
You miss 100% of the steps you don't take.
SQuotes: You've done enough for today. Rest and come back stronger tomorrow.
Be proud of yourself for how far you've come and never forget what you have accomplished.
Don't burn yourself out trying to get there all at once. Remember, it's the journey that matters.
Self-care is giving the world the best of you, instead of what's left of you.
You are enough, just as you are.
Perfection is not attainable, but progress is.
It's okay to take a break, it's okay to rest. You are only human.
The best preparation for tomorrow is doing your best today.
Success is not about how much you accomplish in a day, it's about the journey and the effort you put in every day.
